                  | Рестораны, бары
                +e.feat-item
                  +e('span').feat-icon(style="background-image: url('img/object-feat4.png')")
                  | Банки
                +e.feat-item 
                  +e('span').feat-icon(style="background-image: url('img/object-feat5.png')")
